---
// src/pages/about.astro

import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base"
---

<PageLayout meta={{
  title: "About",
  canonicalURL: "https://javascriptjam.com/about"
}}>
  <main class="main-content post no-image">
    <div class="post-header tc">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="lhtitle font-heading mb1 mt0 fs36">About this site</h1>
        <hr class="line line--center">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container post-content centered mt4">
      <p>JavaScript Jam is an online publication launched by the Community Growth team at Edgio. If you subscribe today, you'll get full access to the website as well as email newsletters about new content when it's available. Your subscription makes this site possible, and allows JavaScript Jam to continue to exist. Thank you!</p>
      <h3 id="fresh-content-delivered">Fresh content, delivered</h3>
      <p>Stay up to date with new content sent straight to your inbox! No more worrying about whether you missed something because of a pesky algorithm or news feed.</p>
      <h3 id="meet-people-like-you">Meet people like you</h3>
      <p>Join a community of other subscribers who share the same interests.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</PageLayout>